<p>10.8     The expenses associated with (a) any risks and ensuing damage to the Vehicle, which are not fully covered<br/>by the Vehicle Insurance; (b) risks which are not borne by the Host in terms hereof shall be borne by the<br/>Guest. Accordingly, the Guest shall pay to the Host the amount of loss and/or damage not paid under the<br/>Vehicle Insurance and be liable for the following:<br/></p>
