<p>                   <b>ii. </b>         Theft/total loss of the Vehicle: (a) The shortfall between the claim amount received under the<br/>Vehicle Insurance, and the book value of the Vehicle at that time of its theft/total loss; (b) if usage of<br/>Vehicle at the time of its theft/total loss exceeds the Agreed Mileage, charge of the excess mileage<br/>incurred as per the rate specified in the Fee Policy ; (c) other cost/expense incurred by the Host for or<br/>in respect of assessment loss suffered by the Vehicle and possibility of its restoration; and (d) other<br/>charges, if any, remaining unpaid by Guest under this Agreement.<br/></p>
